HEADWORD: Predication
<hw>Pred`i*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>praedicatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>pr⟦eacute⟧dication</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of predicating, or of affirming one thing of
